quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,"∆äam nguurndam aduna e ko woni e majjam immorde e tuuyo e dakamme wonaali, si wanaa ko mbelee…óe e fijindaaru …ìer…óe yowitii…ìe e majjam. ∆äum ko ko lannata he√±a. Pellet non, ko ho…óo laakara ngon woni nguurndam …óam tigi, tawde …óam heddotoo. Sinno …ìe annduno, …ìe ardintaano ko lannata kon yeeso ko lannataa kon."
  29,65,"Si …ìe wa…ó…óike ka laana, …ìe noddira Alla la…ì…ìinan- gol Mo Kanko tun noddaandu ndun, no O da…óndira …ìe e yoolagol. Tuma nde O da…óndi …ìe e ngol yoolo- gol, …ìe wa…óta kafidude Mo e rewetee…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  29,66,"∆Åe wa…óti sirkude no …ìe yeddira ko Men okki …ìe kon e neemaaji, awa yo …ìe dakmitor ko Men okki …ìe kon e neweende aduna; ar ma …ìe annda battane bonnere ma…ì…ìe nden tuma …ìe maayata."
  29,67,"E yeddu…ìe neemaaji Alla …óin e dow ma…ì…ìe tuma Alla da…óndunoo…ìe yoolagol …ìen yi'aali neemaaji goo? ∆äin woni: Wonnde Men wa…óanii …ìe hormorde hoolniinde ka …ìe da…óndata ∆¥ii∆¥e ma…ì…ìe e jawle ma…ì…ìe? Ka tawata wo…ó…ìe goo hino yoolora ka woniri, …ìen no waree dahee, rew…ìe e …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe hoynee, jawle ma…ì…ìe ciifee(bifte)? E ko rewete…ói ma…ì…ìe meerente …óin …ói …ìe aa∆¥orta woni ko …ìe gom…óinta …ìe yedda neemaaji Alla …óin …ìe ronka yettude Alla e majji?"
  29,68,"Alaa …ìur…óo too√±irde wa on fefindii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla o dammbira sirku e Makko, maa o fenna goonga ka Nulaa…óo Makko on addi kan. Sikke alaa wonnde ko Jahannama woni ho…óorde yeddu…ìe …ìen e nanndo ma…ì…ìe."
  29,69,"∆Åen tii…ónor…ìe wonkiiji mun fii weltinirgol Men, ma Men hawrindin …ìe e peewal laawol Amen focciingol ngol.Ko pellet, Alla no wonndi e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen ballal, e peewal."
  30,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: yewtere sugu …óee Aayeeje yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-Baqarah."
  30,2,"Faarisiyankoo…ìe …ìen foolii Ruumi'en."
  30,3,"Nde fooleede wa…óii ka Saami ka …ìuri …ìadorde leydi Faarisi ndin. Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen non, …ìaawo …ìe fooleede, …ìe fooloyay kam…ìe kadi."
  30,4,"Ngol kiitol ko wa…ói, ko e dumunna mo hewtaa duu…ìi tati o fawaa e duu…ìi sappo. Ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow ado poolgal Ruumiyakoo…ìe …ìen ngal e …ìaawo maggal. Nden √±alnde nde Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen fooloyta Faarisiyankoo…ìe …ìen, gom…óim…ìe …ìen weltoray."
  30,5,"∆Åe weltorayay ko Alla walliri Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen kon, tawde …ìen ko yim…ìe Defte. Alla no walla on Mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo Mo fooleaake, Hinnotoo…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen."